{{Quote|And one day, Willem came riding back into town. And I buried an axe so deep into Willemâ&euro;&trade;s skull they had to bury him with it. Willemâ&euro;&trade;s horse got me to the Wall and Iâ&euro;&trade;ve been wearing black ever since.|Yoren|What is Dead May Never Die}}
'''Yoren''' is a recurring character in the [[Season 1|first]] and [[Season 2|second]] seasons. He is played by [[Francis Magee]] and debuts in &quot;[[Lord Snow]]&quot;. Yoren was a recruiter for the [[Night's Watch]].

